WEBVTT

00:00.020 --> 00:03.022
<i>Previously on AMC's
"Turn: Washington's Spies"...</i>

00:03.024 --> 00:06.625
In portraying you, I, in fact,
outshined the original.

00:06.627 --> 00:09.161
She's been seen on the arm
of several bachelor officers.

00:09.163 --> 00:10.863
She may be seducing them for secrets.

00:12.166 --> 00:14.834
- What happened to Caleb?
- He was grabbed.

00:14.836 --> 00:17.737
I have evidence that he is
a key rebel spy.

00:17.739 --> 00:20.206
Talmadge the leader, you the career...

00:20.208 --> 00:21.607
Woodhull is cover.

00:21.609 --> 00:23.242
Their pirates took one of ours.

00:23.244 --> 00:24.944
You have ours take one of theirs.

00:24.946 --> 00:27.813
We're gonna go back and kidnap
Judge Woodhull and his son

00:27.815 --> 00:29.821
and trade them for Brewster.

00:35.690 --> 00:38.224
Come on.

00:40.000 --> 00:46.074
